data.description: Perfect one-level living. Move right into this adorable 3-bedroom ranch in Trinity schools. Pretty woodwork throughout gives the home a warm cottage look and feel. Covered front porch, 1 car detached garage, level yard, good overall condition. The garage will need a garage door installed for use beyond extra storage. The versatile floor plan can turn the 3rd bedroom into an office or family room. Convenient location to shopping and highways. Cute and easy to maintain one-level living ready for you to make your home.
